column2: I AM GLAD THAT EVERY ONE DRESS LIKE JOHNNY DEPP AS JACK SPARROW
column34: Everybody knows about the lawsuit between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp. We also know how much trouble he has gone to just to defend himself! Well, I have a proposition. Let's make the 9th of June Worldwide Dress Like Depp Day! (The 9th of June is his birthday) You can dress like his roll Willy Wonka! Or maybe Captain Jack Sparrow! Anything he has played, you can dress as! Let's make this happen guys!
